Backend API

This is the backend API for our application. It is built with Node.js and uses SQLite as its database.
Endpoints
POST /register

Registers a new user to the database.

Request body:

json

{
    "email": "<user-email>",
    "password": "<user-password>"
}

POST /add-comment

Adds a new comment to a file.

Request body:

json

{
    "file": "<file-id>",
    "user": "<user-id>",
    "str": "<comment>"
}

POST /upload-file

Uploads a new file to the database.

Request body:

json

{
    "email": "<user-email>",
    "password": "<user-password>",
    "owner": "<owner-id>"
}

Request files:

json

{
    "file": "<file-data>"
}

Setup

    Clone this repository
    Install dependencies
    Run the server using node server.js

Database

The database is located at ../db/db.db.